data.description: A beautiful two story home over 3000 sq ft located in the heart of Historic Smithville, just minutes from the shops. This home has a custom kitchen with an open concept view into the huge great room with 16 ft vaulted ceilings; A bonus room on the first floor that can also be used as an office.  This home has a full finished basement with too many upgrades to list.  Included in the sale of this home is a custom swing set located in the fenced in yard that backs up to a wildlife refuge.  The property also has a sprinkler system and mature land scaping.  SELLER is also offering 12k back at closing to cover some needed repairs.
